{
  "fixed_xml": "<ITEM>
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Falckeisische Bibel</TITLE>
    <FORMAT>Schweinsleder</FORMAT>
    <PRIZE>12 Gulden</PRIZE>
  </BIBL>
  noch gantz neu in gebunden, oder gegen einem neuen
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Corpore Juris</TITLE>
    <PLACE>Leipziger Edition</PLACE>
  </BIBL>
  zu vertauschen.
</ITEM>",
  "number_of_corrections": 5,
  "explanation": [
    "1. Fixed malformed XML by properly nesting `<BIBL>` tags inside `<ITEM>` and ensuring proper hierarchy.",
    "2. Corrected the escaped Unicode characters (`\u221a\u2020`) to plain text (removed as they were not valid XML content in this context).",
    "3. Fixed the `<FORMAT>` tag content by removing the hyphen (`Schweins-leder` → `Schweinsleder`).",
    "4. Properly closed all tags and ensured correct nesting of `<TITLE>`, `<FORMAT>`, `<PRIZE>`, and `<PLACE>` tags within `<BIBL>`.",
    "5. Added missing closing tags for `<BIBL>` and ensured the text outside `<BIBL>` tags is properly formatted."
  ]
}
